(20, 1, '2020-05-05 01:31:33', '2020-05-04 23:31:33', '<img class=\"size-full wp-image-21 alignleft\" src=\"http://clothing.wts2020.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/logo-5.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"70\" />I like this top. It fits as expected and I purchased my normal medium size. It isnt tight across the chest and Im a 36D. The small would probably be too tight across the \"girls\". The material is typical thin (not too thin), stretchy, kinda flowy juniors tshirt fabric. I\'ve recently purchased tshirts from stores with the same fabric. It is a little long (I\'m 5\'4\") but I can wear it out or tucked in. The criss cross detailing is sewn correctly and hangs evenly which I was concerned about when reading the reviews. I purchased black and I would purchase this tshirt again. It\'s a nice tshirt and I recommend it.', 'Short Sleeve', 'I like this top. It fits as expected and I purchased my normal medium size. It isnt tight across the chest and Im a 36D. The small would probably be too tight across the \"girls\". The material is typical thin (not too thin), stretchy, kinda flowy juniors tshirt fabric. I\'ve recently purchased tshirts from stores with the same fabric. It is a little long (I\'m 5\'4\") but I can wear it out or tucked in. The criss cross detailing is sewn correctly and hangs evenly which I was concerned about when reading the reviews. I purchased black and I would purchase this tshirt again. It\'s a nice tshirt and I recommend it.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'black-short-sleeve', '', '', '2020-05-09 21:44:19', '2020-05-09 19:44:19', '', 0, 'http://clothing.wts2020.net/?post_type=product&#038;p=20', 0, 'product', '', 0),
